  <prompt>
    Deploy all Phase 4 integration changes to the dev environment: deploy BFF API changes via `scripts/Deploy-BffApi.ps1`, rebuild and redeploy SprkChatPane and AnalysisWorkspace web resources via the code-page-deploy skill. Verify the full integrated stack works end-to-end in the deployed environment: SSE streaming, write-back, playbook dispatch, dynamic commands, document upload, and Open in Word.
  </prompt>

  <role>Senior full-stack developer</role>

  <goal>
    All Phase 4 integration fixes are deployed to the dev environment. BFF API is updated with fixed integration code. SprkChatPane and AnalysisWorkspace web resources are updated. End-to-end smoke tests pass in the deployed environment: SSE streaming, write-back to Lexical editor, playbook dispatch dialog handoff, dynamic slash commands, document upload, and Open in Word all work correctly.
  </goal>

