  <context>
    <background>
      Phase 4 integration tasks (050-057) fixed any issues discovered during end-to-end wiring. This deployment task applies all those fixes to the deployed dev environment so that Phase 5 testing can run against the deployed stack rather than local dev servers.
    </background>
    <dependencies>
      Depends on all Phase 4 integration tasks (050-057) being complete. This is the final Phase 4 task.
    </dependencies>
  </context>

  <steps>
    <step order="0">Read bff-deploy SKILL.md to confirm the correct deployment invocation for the BFF API</step>
    <step order="1">Run dotnet build src/server/api/Sprk.Bff.Api/ to verify clean build before deploying</step>
    <step order="2">Deploy BFF API via scripts/Deploy-BffApi.ps1 — verify deployment completes successfully</step>
    <step order="3">Verify BFF health check: GET https://spe-api-dev-67e2xz.azurewebsites.net/healthz returns 200</step>
    <step order="4">Build and deploy SprkChatPane via code-page-deploy skill</step>
    <step order="5">Build and deploy AnalysisWorkspace via code-page-deploy skill</step>
    <step order="6">Publish Dataverse customizations</step>
    <step order="7">Smoke test SSE streaming: send a chat message and verify token-by-token streaming response in deployed SprkChatPane</step>
    <step order="8">Smoke test dynamic commands: open SprkChat and verify slash menu shows grouped categories</step>
    <step order="9">Smoke test document upload: drag a PDF and verify processing feedback appears</step>
    <step order="10">Note any post-deploy issues in notes/058-deploy-phase-4-findings.md</step>
    <step order="11">Update TASK-INDEX.md: change task R2-058 status to completed</step>
  </steps>

  <tools>
    <tool>dotnet</tool>
    <tool>npm</tool>
    <tool>pac</tool>
    <tool>git</tool>
  </tools>

  <outputs>
